Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.streams.vectors

Interface VStream

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<Vector2D>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FilteredVStream, PollingVStream, VFuser
    public interface VStream
extends java.util.function.Supplier<Vector2D>
    A VStream is similar to an IStream, but instead of a stream of doubles, it represents a stream of Vector2Ds.
